lyrics:
[Verse]
Cheeseburgers sizzle on the grill, oh so fine
With that gooey cheese, they make my taste buds shine
Juicy beef patty, seasoned just right
I'm craving that cheeseburger, day and night

[Chorus]
Oh, cheeseburger delight, you're my favorite treat
Melting cheese and toppings piled high, can't be beat
I take a bite, oh, the flavors burst and dance
Cheeseburger love, you've got me in a trance
